7. **ketamine IV 만성 multimodal** = NMDA antagonist + dissociative — sub-anesthetic dose multimodal acute pain (cross-anesthesiology + emergency_medicine).
8. **methadone perioperative** = 만성 multimodal + 만성 long-acting μ-opioid + NMDA antag dual-mechanism. perioperative single-dose paradigm.
9. **K-acute pain + 식약처 framework + 산정특례** = 만성 K-acute pain 임상 framework. KR regulatory + reimbursement landscape.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, acute pain 임상 의미 한정.

